---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
	title="Terms of Use - ResumeLink | Resume & CV Builder"
	description="Read ResumeLink's Terms of Use. Understand your rights and responsibilities when using our free resume and CV builder platform."
	keywords="terms of use,terms of service,legal terms,resume builder terms,CV maker legal,user agreement,ResumeLink legal"
>
	<div class="legal-page">
		<div class="wrapper">
			<header class="page-header">
				<h1>Terms of Use</h1>
				<p class="last-updated">Last updated: August 2025</p>
			</header>

			<main class="legal-content">
				<section>
					<h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
					<p>By accessing and using ResumeLink, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. These Terms of Use govern your use of our free resume and CV builder platform.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
					<p>ResumeLink is a free, open-source platform that currently provides:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Access to professional resume and portfolio templates for browsing and preview</li>
						<li>Template gallery with various design styles</li>
						<li>Information and resources about resume building best practices</li>
						<li>Community-driven template collection</li>
					</ul>
					<p><strong>Current Development Stage:</strong> ResumeLink is currently in its foundational phase. Users cannot directly edit templates online at this time. For personalized resume creation using our templates, please contact us at <a href="mailto:wendy7756@outlook.com">wendy7756@outlook.com</a> with your chosen template and resume content.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>3. User Responsibilities</h2>
					<p>When using ResumeLink, you agree to:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Provide accurate and truthful information in your resume/CV</li>
						<li>Use the service for lawful purposes only</li>
						<li>Respect intellectual property rights of templates and content</li>
						<li>Not use the platform to distribute harmful or illegal content</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
					<p>All resume templates and design elements provided by ResumeLink are open-source and available under applicable licenses. Users retain ownership of their personal resume content and data.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>5. Privacy and Data</h2>
					<p>Since ResumeLink currently operates as a template showcase without user registration or online editing capabilities, we do not collect personal information through the website. For details about our privacy practices, please review our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>6. Service Availability</h2>
					<p>ResumeLink strives to maintain 99% uptime, but we cannot guarantee uninterrupted service. We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of the service with reasonable notice.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
					<p>ResumeLink is provided "as is" without warranties. We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of our resume builder platform or any employment outcomes related to resumes created using our service.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>8. Contact Information</h2>
					<p>If you have questions about these Terms of Use, please contact us at <a href="mailto:wendy7756@outlook.com">wendy7756@outlook.com</a>.</p>
				</section>
			</main>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.legal-page {
		min-height: 100vh;
		padding: 2rem 0;
	}

	.page-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		padding-bottom: 2rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: var(--text-4xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
	}

	.last-updated {
		color: var(--gray-400);
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		margin: 0;
	}

	.legal-content {
		max-width: 65ch;
		margin: 0 auto;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.legal-content section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.legal-content h2 {
		color: var(--gray-100);
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
	}

	.legal-content p {
		color: var(--gray-300);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
	}

	.legal-content ul {
		color: var(--gray-300);
		margin: 1rem 0;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
	}

	.legal-content li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.legal-content a {
		color: var(--accent-regular);
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.legal-content a:hover {
		color: var(--accent-dark);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.legal-page {
			padding: 1rem 0;
		}

		.page-header {
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.page-header h1 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
